---
description: Enforce static-only patterns for GitHub Pages hosting
globs:
  - "ui_kits/**/*.html"
  - "ui_kits/**/*.js"
  - "ui_kits/**/*.jsx"
alwaysApply: true
---

- This repository must remain compatible with GitHub Pages static hosting.
- Do not introduce server-side runtime features in dashboard code paths.
- Do not add API route assumptions or server middleware dependencies for page rendering.
- Use relative links and asset paths. Avoid root-absolute URL patterns like `href="/..."`, `src="/..."`, or `fetch("/...")`.
- Do not add SPA routing that depends on host-level rewrite/fallback rules.
- Every navigable page should resolve to a real checked-in HTML file.
